tal result. These are the\neffects of the monopoles and instantons in QCD.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 12 Jul 2018 20:23:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 17 Jun 2019 17:20:38 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 12 Jul 2020 20:44:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-23"}
