 to Witt vectors,\nusing divided powers and polynomial laws. In particular, we produce a natural\nsurjection $W_2 \\circ W_r \\longrightarrow W_{r+1}$, of ring schemes over\n$\\mathbb{F}_p$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 12 Jul 2018 23:16:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 8 Oct 2018 14:03:15 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 24 Nov 2018 22:19:36 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 7 May 2021 14:50:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-05-10"}
