 problem. In\naddition, our approach allows for the direct computation of corresponding\ncredible bands without simulation. We use our technique to estimate bivariate\nnormal distributions and deconvolve BAC/BrAC from TAC based on data from a\npopulation that consists of multiple drinking episodes from a single subject\nand a population consisting of single drinking episodes from multiple subjects.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 13 Jul 2018 13:56:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-12-05"}
